Package Array.layoutFX

Class StreamerProperty

java.lang.Object
Array.layoutFX.StreamerProperty
public class StreamerProperty extends Object
Property class for a Streamer. Create property bindings for certain Streamer values which allows for much easier integration into UI components in JavaFX.
Author:
Jamie Macaulay
